						<summary>

						<p>This is a mere fragment of an inscription mentioning Uḍaiyār <hi rend="bold">Madhurāṉtakan Śundaraśōḻaṉ.</hi> Reference is made to a woman servant of the royal palace by name Kaḷḷichchi Uttama cha•••••••• and one Pūdi Paṭṭālakaṉ Nakka••••• and also to two classes of smiths (<hi rend="italic">Kottar</hi>) of Koḍumbāḷūr.</p>						

						</summary>
