<p>
<lb n="1"/>—uṭaiyār maturāṉtakaṉ cuntaracoḻaṉāṉa—
<lb n="2"/>—veḷattup peṇṭāṭṭi kaḷḷicci Uttama ca—
<lb n="3"/>— <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ṟantāṉ <hi rend="grantha">sū <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> </hi> pūtipaṭṭālakaṉ na<unclear>k</unclear>ka <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vaṟku kā—
<lb n="4"/>— koṭumpāḷūr Iraṇṭuvakai kottaṟkum Iruntu Ārā<supplied reason="omitted">y</supplied>ntu <unclear>I</unclear>ṉṉai—
</p>

